extends layout

block content
  h1 FreeCodeCamp API Basejump: Image Search Abstraction Layer
  br
  h3 User stories:
  p I can get the image URLs, alt text and page urls for a set of images relating to a given search string.
  p I can paginate through the responses by adding a ?offset=2 parameter to the URL.
  p I can get a list of the most recently submitted search strings

  h3 Example usage:
  code https://kevinimgsearch.herokuapp.com/latest/imgsearch
  br
  code https://kevinimgsearch.herokuapp.com/imgsearch/some_search_term?offset=2

  h3 Example output:
  code { searchTerm: "dog", time: "Fri Jul 22 2016 22:07:51 GMT+0930 (ACST)" }
  br
  code { url: "http://i.imgur.com/ikzPcK3.gif", alt_text: "Cat fail big time" }